Show HN: I made an iOS app for HN instant browsing with searchable favorites
text:
Hi, I made this app a few weeks ago, to solve the following problems: instantly browse HN stories and "hop" from story to story ; save and search favorites (which you can use to save a story for later reading)

As a bonus, the app also works on Mac.

Sometimes the title of a story doesn't do justice to the content, and this app makes sure you never miss an interesting one.
